file: tmp_【#マリン船長の番組】2周年記念に地獄企画いくつかやりました【ホロライブ⧸宝鐘マリン】 [tV0vI7Aflho]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_005.mov

scenes.description: Houshou Marine is in the middle of a frantic VR ramen shop simulation, struggling with the fast pace and multiple orders.
Marine stops her failed run, explains that she picked the wrong mode, and notices a timer on the desk before restarting the 5-minute challenge.
Marine begins her final 5-minute challenge, frantically cooking ramen and gyoza while managing various customers, including a robot and a very hungry man.
